<package version="1.0">
  <name>PEAR</name>
  <summary>PEAR Base System</summary>
  <description>The PEAR package contains:
 * the PEAR base class
 * the PEAR_Error error handling mechanism
 * the PEAR installer, for creating, distributing
   and installing packages</description>
